-How do you do, Mr. Pike?
-No, Mother, "Smike," with an "S."

998
01:15:05,835 --> 01:15:08,827
-How do you do?
-Very well, thank you, Mr. Spike.

999
01:15:11,307 --> 01:15:13,468
And this is our Iandlady, Miss Lacreevy.

1000
01:15:13,576 --> 01:15:16,010
