a miniature of you.

1002
01:15:22,618 --> 01:15:26,076
Kate, this is my faithful friend
and fellow traveler.

1003
01:15:27,156 --> 01:15:28,680
I have been so eager...

1004
01:15:28,758 --> 01:15:31,556
