1055
01:19:41,810 --> 01:19:45,746
as well as by the rapidity
with which you ate that cake...

1056
01:19:46,348 --> 01:19:49,977
we'd Iike to begin you on a salary
of ￡1 20 a year.

1057
01:19:55,057 --> 01:19:56,684
