1063
01:20:18,681 --> 01:20:20,672
-Are you at home?
-Yes.

1064
01:20:20,883 --> 01:20:22,214
-To anybody?
-Yes.

1065
01:20:22,351 --> 01:20:24,683
-To the tax gatherer?
-No.

1066
01:20:24,820 --> 01:20:26,287
What about....

1067
01:20:29,491 --> 01:20:31,322
I'd know your face anywhere.

1068
01:20:31,460 --> 01:20:34,691
You'd know it better
if your nephew hadn't maltreated it.

1069
01:20:35,631 --> 01:20:36,791
Who is this?

1070
01:20:37,266 --> 01:20:39,234
My son, Iittle Wackford.

1071
01:20:39,968 --> 01:20:42,960
Indeed a specimen
of the Dotheboys's old diet.

1072
01:20:43,205 --> 01:20:45,196
A miracle of high feeding.

1073
01:20:45,941 --> 01:20:48,136
His flesh, his firmness.

1074
01:20:50,012 --> 01:20:51,070
No tears.

1075
01:20:51,814 --> 01:20:53,281
His oiliness.

1076
01:20:53,382 --> 01:20:55,111
I'd expect nothing Iess.

1077
01:20:56,585 --> 01:20:59,850
And Mrs. Squeers, how is....

1078
01:21:00,255 --> 01:21:04,749
Mrs. Squeers is as she always is.
A joy to all them as knows her.

1079
