1085
01:21:23,245 --> 01:21:24,212
Noggs...

1086
01:21:24,279 --> 01:21:26,770
-see this package?
-It's big enough.

1087
01:21:26,915 --> 01:21:28,906
Take it, please, at once.

1088
01:21:29,852 --> 01:21:32,252
"Take it, please, at once."

1089
01:21:32,688 --> 01:21:36,089
"At once, do you hear? If not sooner."

1090
01:21:38,260 --> 01:21:39,887
