1093
01:21:48,137 --> 01:21:50,230
to your troubles, though...

1094
01:21:51,206 --> 01:21:52,798
it seems foolish...

1095
01:21:53,375 --> 01:21:55,172
if the boy is unpunished.

1096
01:21:55,244 --> 01:21:57,212
He might come after you again.

1097
01:21:57,346 --> 01:21:59,473
Surely he's been punished by you.

1098
01:21:59,581 --> 01:22:00,741
Our ties have been cut.

1099
01:22:00,849 --> 01:22:03,818
