that he views that as a punishment.

1100
01:22:05,220 --> 01:22:06,949
What about the other boy?

1101
01:22:07,055 --> 01:22:08,522
-Smike?
-Yes.

1102
01:22:10,225 --> 01:22:13,592
You said that my nephew
was quite attached to him.

1103
01:22:14,263 --> 01:22:15,924
What do you know of him?

1104
01:22:16,265 --> 01:22:19,234
Only that he came to us 1 2 or so years ago.

1105
01:22:19,368 --> 01:22:22,599
