of usefulness on his part.

1108
01:22:29,711 --> 01:22:31,611
-No parents then?
-No.

1109
01:22:31,680 --> 01:22:34,148
-No person with any claim on him?
-No.

1110
01:22:35,284 --> 01:22:36,808
So he's yours.

1111
01:22:37,286 --> 01:22:38,685
And he's been stolen.

1112
01:22:38,754 --> 01:22:41,222
Would it not be well within your rights
to take him?

1113
01:22:41,323 --> 01:22:44,019
