to join me on my errands.

1118
01:23:01,643 --> 01:23:02,940
Ribbons for sale.

1119
01:23:03,178 --> 01:23:05,544
-Oh, dear.
-What is it?

1120
01:23:05,914 --> 01:23:07,006
Father used to tell me...

1121
01:23:07,149 --> 01:23:10,141
