he would buy me some as a remembrance.

1123
01:23:16,124 --> 01:23:18,058
Ribbons for sale.

1124
01:23:25,133 --> 01:23:26,259
How much, please?

1125
01:23:26,335 --> 01:23:28,565
Twopence for the pink ones.
Penny for the others.

1126
01:23:28,637 --> 01:23:30,332
