your matching half?

1218
01:31:23,979 --> 01:31:26,948
Then we must think of how to find her.

1219
01:31:27,382 --> 01:31:30,374
For when she knows you,
she will Iove you, too.

1220
01:31:31,586 --> 01:31:35,454
